vernac_cmds: Definition disjoint (A B : part_set E) := Equal (inter A B) (empty E).
Lemma disjoint_comp : forall A A' B B' : part_set E, Equal A A' -> Equal B B' -> disjoint A B -> disjoint A' B'.
intros A A' B B' H' H'0 H'1; try assumption.
Lemma empty_not_in : forall A : part_set E, Equal A (empty E) -> forall x : E, ~ in_part x A.
intros A; case A; intros a pa; simpl in |- *.
unfold eq_part, empty in |- *; simpl in |- *.
Lemma disjoint_inclus : forall A B C : part_set E, included A B -> disjoint B C -> disjoint A C.
intros A B C H' H'0; try assumption.
Lemma included_add_part : forall (A : part_set E) (x : E), included A (add_part A x).
Lemma union_not_in : forall (A B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x A -> ~ in_part x B -> ~ in_part x (union A B).
cut (in_part x A \/ in_part x B).
Lemma disjoint_not_in_r : forall (A B : part_set E) (x : E), disjoint A B -> in_part x A -> ~ in_part x B.
Lemma cardinal_union_disjoint : forall (a b : nat) (A B : part_set E), cardinal A a -> cardinal B b -> disjoint A B -> cardinal (union A B) (a + b).
apply cardinal_comp_l with (union (empty E) B); auto with *.
apply cardinal_comp_l with B; auto with *.
apply cardinal_add with (union B0 B) x; auto with *.
apply disjoint_inclus with (add_part B0 x); auto with *.
apply disjoint_comp with A B; auto with *.
apply disjoint_not_in_r with A; auto with *.
apply in_part_comp_r with (add_part B0 x); auto with *.
apply Trans with (union (add_part B0 x) B); auto with *.
apply Trans with (union B0 (union (single x) B)); auto with *.
apply Trans with (union B0 (union B (single x))); auto with *.
Lemma in_eq_part : forall A B : part_set E, (forall x : E, in_part x A -> in_part x B) -> (forall x : E, in_part x B -> in_part x A) -> Equal A B.
case A; case B; simpl in |- *.
Lemma diff_in_l : forall (A B : part_set E) (x : E), in_part x (diff A B) -> in_part x A.
case A; case B; simpl in |- *.
Lemma diff_in_r : forall (A B : part_set E) (x : E), in_part x (diff A B) -> ~ in_part x B.
case A; case B; simpl in |- *.
Lemma in_diff : forall (A B : part_set E) (x : E), in_part x A -> ~ in_part x B -> in_part x (diff A B).
case A; case B; simpl in |- *.
Lemma union_diff : forall A B : part_set E, Equal (union A (diff B A)) (union A B).
Lemma disjoint_diff : forall A B : part_set E, disjoint A (diff B A).
intros x; red in |- *; intros H'; try exact H'.
apply in_part_inter_r with A; auto with *.
apply in_part_inter_l with (diff B A); auto with *.
Lemma cardinal_union : forall (a b : nat) (A B : part_set E), cardinal A a -> cardinal (diff B A) b -> cardinal (union A B) (a + b).
apply cardinal_comp_l with (union A (diff B A)); auto with *.
Lemma empty_diff : forall A : part_set E, Equal (diff (empty E) A) (empty E).
apply diff_in_l with A; auto with *.
Lemma empty_inter : forall A : part_set E, Equal (inter (empty E) A) (empty E).
apply in_part_inter_l with A; auto with *.
Lemma in_part_trans_eq : forall (A : part_set E) (x y : E), in_part x A -> Equal y x -> in_part y A.
intros A; case A; simpl in |- *.
intros x y H' H'0; try assumption.
apply pa with x; auto with *.
Lemma diff_add_part : forall (A B0 B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x B0 -> Equal A (add_part B0 x) -> in_part x B -> Equal (diff B0 B) (diff A B).
intros A B0 B x H' H'0 H'1; try assumption.
apply diff_in_l with B; auto with *.
apply diff_in_r with B0; auto with *.
apply diff_in_r with A; auto with *.
apply in_part_trans_eq with x0; auto with *.
apply add_part_in_el_diff with x; auto with *.
apply in_part_comp_r with A; auto with *.
apply diff_in_l with B; auto with *.
apply diff_in_r with A; auto with *.
Lemma diff_not_in : forall (A B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x A -> ~ in_part x (diff A B).
apply diff_in_l with B; auto with *.
Lemma inter_not_in : forall (A B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x A -> ~ in_part x (inter A B).
apply in_part_inter_l with B; auto with *.
Lemma inter_add_part : forall (A B0 B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x B0 -> Equal A (add_part B0 x) -> in_part x B -> Equal (inter A B) (add_part (inter B0 B) x).
intros A B0 B x H' H'0 H'1; try assumption.
apply Trans with (inter (union B0 (single x)) B).
apply Trans with (union (inter B0 B) (inter (single x) B)).
apply in_part_inter_l with B; auto with *.
apply in_part_trans_eq with x; auto with *.
Lemma diff_add_part_not_in : forall (A B0 B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x B0 -> Equal A (add_part B0 x) -> ~ in_part x B -> Equal (diff A B) (add_part (diff B0 B) x).
intros A B0 B x H' H'0 H'1; try assumption.
apply in_part_trans_eq with x; auto with *.
apply add_part_in_el_diff with x; auto with *.
apply in_part_comp_r with A; auto with *.
apply diff_in_l with B; auto with *.
apply diff_in_r with A; auto with *.
apply in_part_comp_r with (add_part B0 x); auto with *.
apply in_part_trans_eq with x; auto with *.
apply diff_in_l with B; auto with *.
apply in_part_trans_eq with x0; auto with *.
apply diff_in_r with B0; auto with *.
apply add_part_in_el_diff with x; auto with *.
Lemma inter_add_part_not_in : forall (A B0 B : part_set E) (x : E), ~ in_part x B0 -> Equal A (add_part B0 x) -> ~ in_part x B -> Equal (inter B0 B) (inter A B).
intros A B0 B x H' H'0 H'1; try assumption.
apply Trans with (inter (union B0 (single x)) B).
apply Trans with (union (inter B0 B) (inter (single x) B)).
apply Trans with (union (inter B0 B) (empty E)).
apply in_part_trans_eq with x0; auto with *.
Lemma cardinal_diff : forall (a : nat) (A B : part_set E), cardinal A a -> exists b : nat, (exists c : nat, cardinal (diff A B) b /\ cardinal (inter A B) c /\ a = b + c).
apply Trans with (diff (empty E) B); auto with *.
apply Trans with (inter (empty E) B); auto with *.
apply cardinal_comp_l with (diff B0 B); auto with *.
apply diff_add_part with x; auto with *.
apply cardinal_add with (inter B0 B) x; auto with *.
apply cardinal_add with (diff B0 B) x; auto with *.
apply cardinal_comp_l with (inter B0 B); auto with *.
apply inter_add_part_not_in with x; auto with *.
Lemma cardinal_union_inter : forall (A B : part_set E) (a b c : nat), cardinal A a -> cardinal B b -> cardinal (inter A B) c -> cardinal (union A B) (a + b - c).
apply cardinal_comp with (union A (diff B A)) (a + x); auto with *.
replace (a + x + x0) with (x0 + (a + x)); auto with *.
apply cardinal_comp_l with (inter A B); auto with *.
